reviews: This is one powerful fan. The highest setting is almost too much. I love it. I purchased this for white noise whilst sleeping and it is incredible. I find too many fans these days are all about their quietness. I don't want a quiet fan. I want a fan that will block noise. If you are getting a fan for sleeping/white noise, look no further.

review_title: High quality and HUGE when expanded.
reviews: Every part of this bag feel very high quality from the material on the bag itself, the fixtures, and the strap. I used the bag last week and was able to fit a week's worth of clothes with a pair of shoes, sandals, toiletries, a towel and some misc. items. Highly recommend.

review_title: I think there must have been an issue with a batch of these shirts...
reviews: Big fan or Carhartt. I love every product of theirs that I own. I am only putting this rating up to hopefully have someone investigate a potential product issue. I believe that a bunch of 3XL shirts in black were mislabelled or some other defect. I have initiated a return for this product. If you check the picture I uploaded the grey shirt is a normal 3XL, the black shirt is also labelled as 3XL, but you'll notice it is significantly smaller. Another review commented with the same issue, so I would be wary of ordering this shirt in black until this issue is solved and the erroneous products are replaced. I own a bunch of Carhartt items in this size and the Carhartt Mens Big & Tall Workwear Pocket Short-Sleeve T-Shirt Original Fit K87 has been the only one way off in size, which leads me to believe there is a mislabel. Thanks!
I have purchased these previously and absolutely love them. They are the most comfortable slip on sandals I have ever owned. Highly recommend them.

I was looking for a big towel, and this is a ridiculously big towel. Someone else mentioned that it could be a blanket, and that is true. It is very soft, and very absorbent. I will be buying more of these as I need to phase towels out.

Perhaps I'm a Luddite, but I still prefer wired headphones to wireless headphones, and I use an Aux cable in my car. This has been a life saver to allow me to charge my phone whilst using wired headphones or an aux cable. So far I have had no issues. The sound quality has been fine when charging or not charging. I saw other complaints about a buzz, but I have not experienced that.

reviews: I have been a big fan of the Daily show since 2001, so I was already in the target demographic for this book. I really enjoyed it! It was a great behind the scenes look at the journey of the show. Highly recommend.

reviews: This was exactly what I was looking for but couldn't find in stores locally. I am very pleased with the holder. It is very sturdy and easily manipulated.

I've only had this for about a week, but thus far I am a big fan. I found that it charges my phone (Samsung Galaxy Nexus) faster than my actual phone charger from Samsung, so that was a little surprising. I've been able to get around 1.5 full charges of my phone out of it before having to recharge the charger.

I found that I could easily have the phone and charger in my jeans pocket whilst the phone was being charged, which I was very happy about.

I did a test with an iPhone as well and the charger also charged that phone faster than the Apple charger.

I foolishly didn't realize that the charger was available in different colours and would likely have gone with black if I had realized, but the blue finish looks great as well.

All in all I am very happy with this product. Thanks Anker!
